PMID- 39093098
OWN - NLM
STAT- MEDLINE
DCOM- 20241109
LR  - 20241205
IS  - 1878-7401 (Electronic)
IS  - 0928-7329 (Print)
IS  - 0928-7329 (Linking)
VI  - 32
